Value NEIGHBOR_NAME (\S+)
Value LOCAL_INTERFACE (.+?)
Value NEIGHBOR_INTERFACE (.+?)
Value MANAGEMENT_IP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value PLATFORM (.+?)
Value CAPABILITY (.+?)

Start
  ^Device\s+ID:\s+${NEIGHBOR_NAME} -> Continue
  ^\s+IP\s+address:\s+${MANAGEMENT_IP}
  ^Platform:\s+${PLATFORM}\s*,\s*Capabilities:\s+${CAPABILITY}
  ^Interface:\s+${LOCAL_INTERFACE}\s*,\s*Port\s+ID\s+\(outgoing\s+port\):\s+${NEIGHBOR_INTERFACE} -> Record
